Package com.ibm.avatar.algebra.datamodel

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractTupleSchema
    Object that encapsulates the shared schema of a set of tuples.
    FieldCopier
    Reusable accessor class for copying fields from one tuple to another.
    FieldGetter<ft>
    Reusable accessor object for retrieving a field from a tuple.
    FieldSetter<ft>
    Reusable accessor object for setting a field in a tuple.
    FieldType
    This class encapsulates the data type of a field in a Tuple object.
    Pair<firstT,secondT>
    An ordered pair, for example, the STL pair class.
    ScalarList<st>
    The ScalarList provides a container for an ordered bag of scalar objects.
    Span
    Object that encapsulates a span over text.
    Text
    Wrapper for raw document text that provides the Span API.
    TextGetter
    Special accessor for getting Text objects from a Text or Span field.
    TextSetter
    Special accessor for setting text fields.
    TLIter
    An iterator over a TupleList.
    Triple<firstT,secondT,thirdT>
    An ordered triple
    Tuple
    Reference-counted object that holds the fields of a tuple.
    TupleList
    This class provides a container for an ordered bag of Tuple objects.
    TupleSchema
    This class encapsulates the "real" schema of an operator.
